      "description": "CFD-predicted relative hemolysis indices (RH) were compared against measured RH values from the observational registry. Across all 5 flow-speed operating points, CFD predictions fell within ±12% of measured means (mean absolute error 0.08 RH units). All CFD predictions satisfied RH < 1.0; measured values confirmed this in 46 of 47 procedures. The validation team concluded that CFD predictions are adequately corroborated by the empirical evidence, supporting acceptance of the model for the intended COU.",
      "wasGeneratedBy": "https://uofa.net/synth/activity/cpb-hemolysis-validation-study",
      "validationMetric": "Relative Hemolysis Index (RH)",
